<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style>
body{
	font-family:Calibri, Arial;
	font-size: 11pt;
	width: 100%;
	text-align: left;
    color:rgba(23, 29, 35, 0.74);
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px
}
td{
    padding-left: 20px;
}
.imageClass{
	padding-top:10px;
}
</style>
	<body style="font-size:95%;">
<div style="text-align: right; padding-right:5px;">
<img src='https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmRe&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493805474000'/>
</div>
<br/>
		Dear {!Product__c.First_Name__c},
		<br/><br/>
		We know you take your credit seriously, however your Affirm Mastercard® account is currently past due. Your credit card charging privileges have now been suspended until a payment is received. The minimum payment required is <strong> {!Product__c.Minimum_Payment_Amount__c} </strong>. 
		<br/><br/>
		<strong>
		Choose one of our convenient payment options listed below: 
		</strong>
		<br>
		<table style="padding-left:10px;margin-top:4px">
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass">
					<img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPA&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/>
				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Set up a one-time bill payment through your online banking. Just add Payee: “Affirm Mastercard” or pay directly at your local bank.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass"> <img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPC&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/>
				</td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Visit a Western Union with a Western Union Quick Collect (WUQC). Use “Affirm Canada” for code city, “BC” for code Province.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass"><img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmP9&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/></td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Mail a cheque to: Affirm Card, PO Box 48235, Vancouver, BC, V7X 1A1.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="imageClass"><img src="https://c.na55.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015f1000001YmPB&oid=00Dj0000001ripe&lastMod=1493803763000" alt="Company Logo" height="40" width="40"/></td>
<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Pay online using TelPay at TelPay.ca.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<br><br><br>
		If you are experiencing payment difficulties, we will gladly talk with you about payment options that may allow you to use your card. To discuss payment arrangements, please contact us at <strong>1-855-266-3131</strong>. Hours of operation are as follows:
		<br><br>
		<div style="text-align: center;">
			Monday-Thursday 8:00 AM-7:00 PM EST <br>
			Friday 8:00 AM-6:00 PM EST<br>
			Saturday 9:00 AM-5:00 PM EST<br>
		</div>
		<br><br>
		Making consistent on time minimum payments is very important to your credit score. A past due payment will have a negative impact on your credit rating and your ability to obtain future credit.
		<br><br><br>
		Sincerely,
		<br><br>
		Affirm Financial Services <br>
		1-855-266-3131<br>
		<br><br>
		<div style="font-size: 11px;">
			If your records reflect that you paid this payment prior to the date of this email please contact us so that the discrepancy can be resolved and any necessary corrections made on your account. Note that payments made using non-guaranteed funds may not create available credit on your account for up to 7 days to allow the payment to clear. Please see your Cardholder Agreement for the full terms on your account. You are receiving this email as per the agreed upon terms in your Cardholder Agreement.
		</div>
		<br>
		<div style="text-align: center; background-color: #115995; color: #dbe3eb;font-size: 10px;padding: 4px;">
			Affirm Mastercard®. This card is issued by Peoples Trust Company under licence from Mastercard International.
			<br>
			®/TM Mastercard is a registered trademark, and the circles design is a trademark of Mastercard International Incorporated.
		</div>
	</body>
</html>